{"about_the_game":"Welcome into the realm of ELVERA, an Indie Third-Person PvP Action Game developed by a single developer. The game is completely free-to-play with no monetization, where player choice and strategy shape their experience.<br><br>From the mind of one, for the community of many, ELVERA offers a rich, evolving world where two factions fight for dominance. Each match is a fresh challenge, shaped by the unique abilities of a diverse roster of heroes, several unique events that happen during rounds and your strategy choices.<br><br>ELVERA stands out with its signature Twinbytes and Manifestation mechanic, inviting players to engage in a strategic dance of deception and unpredictability.<br><br>Free to all, ELVERA provides a balanced battlefield where tactics, not transactions, lead to triumph.<br><br>Join the Early Access on Steam, contribute to ELVERA's growth, and be part of our small, yet passionate community.<br><br><strong>Discord</strong> - <br><strong>Twitter</strong> - <br><strong>YouTube</strong> - ","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Abra-Cadabra-Not","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2018820/1e89b20ca5b69554500b1643105b366f9ec2a54e.jpg"},{"name":"Who's Carrying Now?!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2018820/6ead640c10fc2a3916e92cd85d76dda73de8406a.jpg"},{"name":"Absolute Pacifist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2018820/4f0cbdd7aab33348c663a2e42bd088adca1dd2e3.jpg"},{"name":"404: Competition Not Found","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2018820/38b1e7931baa032c14af1cacb5b392599f70249a.jpg"},{"name":"Who's Counting? Oh, Right, Me.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2018820/5b297c2752f782c4c03a1cba9b7810ff16900b3f.jpg"}],"total":5},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2018820/page_bg_